Class MyObject

java.lang.Object
MyObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
MyAsteroid, MyMoon, MyPlanet, MySun
public class MyObject
extends java.lang.Object
Superclass of all other classes which represent any kind of solar object. Holds the basic necessary variables for building a solar object.
